1
00:00:38,420 --> 00:00:41,060
=How to Train Your Killer=

2
00:00:41,060 --> 00:00:43,900
=Episode 28=

3
00:01:22,840 --> 00:01:23,840
Lingsan,

4
00:01:24,950 --> 00:01:28,480
I finally avenged you.

5
00:01:36,070 --> 00:01:37,480
Qingyao, Qingyao.

6
00:01:37,790 --> 00:01:39,310
Wake up, Qingyao.

7
00:01:39,310 --> 00:01:40,200
Wake up.

8
00:01:40,870 --> 00:01:42,510
Qingyao, you're awake.

9
00:01:42,840 --> 00:01:44,510
Qingyao, are you alright?

10
00:01:45,190 --> 00:01:46,520
- Qingyao.
- Your Majesty.

11
00:01:46,870 --> 00:01:48,150
We've switched back.

12
00:01:51,230 --> 00:01:52,070
Qingyao.

13
00:01:53,230 --> 00:01:54,070
Are you unharmed?

14
00:01:58,590 --> 00:01:59,430
Your Majesty.

15
00:02:15,910 --> 00:02:16,750
Guards!

16
00:02:17,310 --> 00:02:18,960
Detain the assassins in prison

17
00:02:20,150 --> 00:02:21,870
pending trial.

18
00:02:23,360 --> 00:02:25,400
- Yes, Your Majesty.
- Shiyi...

19
00:02:27,310 --> 00:02:28,630
I should have known all along.

20
00:02:28,910 --> 00:02:29,750
He...

21
00:02:30,120 --> 00:02:30,960
Your Highness.

22
00:02:31,190 --> 00:02:32,120
Go!

23
00:02:32,120 --> 00:02:34,360
Assassinating the emperor in any dynasty

24
00:02:34,570 --> 00:02:35,800
is a crime punishable by death.

25
00:02:36,240 --> 00:02:37,280
That law is absolute.

26
00:02:37,600 --> 00:02:38,520
No, it's not like that.

27
00:02:38,780 --> 00:02:39,630
Your Majesty.

28
00:02:39,630 --> 00:02:42,190
Shiyi, Shiyi!

29
00:02:46,470 --> 00:02:49,400
Qingyao, Qingyao, Qingyao!

30
00:03:13,870 --> 00:03:15,710
Your Highness, you're awake.

31
00:03:17,080 --> 00:03:18,470
Am I dreaming?

32
00:03:20,000 --> 00:03:21,030
No, this isn't a dream.

33
00:03:21,280 --> 00:03:22,150
Have you forgotten?

34
00:03:22,150 --> 00:03:23,910
An assassin broke into yesterday.

35
00:03:23,910 --> 00:03:25,310
It was His Majesty who saved you.

36
00:03:26,240 --> 00:03:27,120
Where is the assassin?

37
00:03:27,120 --> 00:03:28,280
One is dead.

38
00:03:28,430 --> 00:03:29,800
The other's locked in the dungeon.

39
00:03:30,000 --> 00:03:31,710
I heard he's to be executed soon.

40
00:03:32,240 --> 00:03:33,240
Where is Ling Yu?

41
00:03:33,300 --> 00:03:34,990
His Majesty is tied up
with state affairs.

42
00:03:35,190 --> 00:03:37,560
He even spoke of crowning you
the Empress.

43
00:03:38,630 --> 00:03:40,120
I have no wish to be an Empress.

44
00:03:40,120 --> 00:03:41,000
I want to see Ling Yu.

45
00:03:41,960 --> 00:03:44,120
Please take care.

46
00:03:46,000 --> 00:03:46,910
His Majesty!

47
00:03:46,910 --> 00:03:48,520
Your Highness, please lower your voice.

48
00:03:48,700 --> 00:03:50,480
The Emperor is engaged
with official matters.

49
00:03:50,680 --> 00:03:52,310
He may not have time to see you for now.

50
00:03:52,710 --> 00:03:53,520
Step aside.

51
00:03:53,520 --> 00:03:55,180
I'm looking for the Emperor.
Your Majesty!

52
00:03:55,180 --> 00:03:56,750
Move! Make way.

53
00:03:56,750 --> 00:03:57,630
Your Majesty!

54
00:03:58,630 --> 00:04:01,350
Your Highness, mind your words
and actions.

55
00:04:01,610 --> 00:04:03,990
Do not think that just because
you have His Majesty's favor,

56
00:04:04,360 --> 00:04:05,910
you can do whatever you please.

57
00:04:05,910 --> 00:04:06,840
You!

58
00:04:07,710 --> 00:04:08,870
Wait here.

59
00:04:53,390 --> 00:04:54,240
Your Majesty.

60
00:04:54,390 --> 00:04:55,800
Qingyao, you want to see me?

61
00:04:57,750 --> 00:04:58,600
Your Majesty,

62
00:04:58,600 --> 00:05:00,270
Shiyi never meant to harm you.

63
00:05:00,430 --> 00:05:01,950
He was forced by others before.

64
00:05:01,950 --> 00:05:03,000
He had no other choice.

65
00:05:04,600 --> 00:05:06,430
Being coerced still makes him
an accomplice.

66
00:05:06,820 --> 00:05:08,390
An accomplice assassinating the Emperor,

67
00:05:08,800 --> 00:05:10,630
you should know what that means.

68
00:05:13,800 --> 00:05:14,720
But...

69
00:05:15,360 --> 00:05:17,480
He did help you suppress the rebellion

70
00:05:17,770 --> 00:05:18,770
and rendered great merit.

71
00:05:19,510 --> 00:05:20,560
I beg you, please.

72
00:05:21,920 --> 00:05:23,070
Spare him, I beg you.

73
00:05:24,870 --> 00:05:26,310
Merit cannot offset his crimes.

74
00:05:26,650 --> 00:05:28,630
If not for concern over your health
at the time,

75
00:05:29,160 --> 00:05:30,720
I would have dealt with him long ago.

76
00:05:35,620 --> 00:05:36,950
What is the reasoning behind this?

77
00:05:38,000 --> 00:05:39,560
Why must you insist on taking his life?

78
00:05:39,560 --> 00:05:40,410
Why?

79
00:05:40,410 --> 00:05:41,430
Gu Qingyao.

80
00:05:42,070 --> 00:05:43,040
Do not forget

81
00:05:43,920 --> 00:05:45,800
the one pulling the strings
is Gu Pingzhang.

82
00:05:46,630 --> 00:05:48,870
Letting your father go
is already my limit.

83
00:05:49,830 --> 00:05:51,480
Do not push beyond your bounds.

84
00:05:55,480 --> 00:05:56,750
He's right.

85
00:05:57,480 --> 00:05:58,320
You're afraid of him.

86
00:06:00,680 --> 00:06:02,600
Would I fear a mere assassin?

87
00:06:02,600 --> 00:06:03,680
You do fear him.

88
00:06:04,560 --> 00:06:05,720
These past days,

89
00:06:06,240 --> 00:06:07,600
you keep recalling the night

90
00:06:07,600 --> 00:06:09,190
he tried to assassinate you.

91
00:06:09,830 --> 00:06:10,600
Only if he's gone,

92
00:06:10,600 --> 00:06:11,800
will you truly sleep in peace.

93
00:06:11,800 --> 00:06:12,650
Am I right?

94
00:06:12,650 --> 00:06:13,550
Silence!

95
00:06:13,800 --> 00:06:14,680
Gu Qingyao,

96
00:06:15,830 --> 00:06:16,800
do not think

97
00:06:19,510 --> 00:06:21,310
I would truly dare not end your life.

98
00:06:23,040 --> 00:06:24,040
Then do it.

99
00:06:25,310 --> 00:06:26,240
Go ahead!

100
00:06:29,870 --> 00:06:30,710
Gu Qingyao,

101
00:06:31,950 --> 00:06:33,390
tell me why.

102
00:06:34,600 --> 00:06:36,430
He's merely a lowly guard.

103
00:06:36,800 --> 00:06:38,660
Is he really worth giving up
being the Empress

104
00:06:38,660 --> 00:06:39,830
and willingly dying for?

105
00:06:43,190 --> 00:06:44,030
Empress?

106
00:06:50,270 --> 00:06:51,720
In your eyes,

107
00:06:53,120 --> 00:06:54,560
women in the Palace

108
00:06:55,270 --> 00:06:56,950
are nothing but ornaments to the throne.

109
00:06:58,070 --> 00:06:59,360
For the sake of power,

110
00:06:59,800 --> 00:07:01,390
there's nothing you wouldn't sacrifice.

111
00:07:04,070 --> 00:07:05,390
In your eyes,

112
00:07:06,920 --> 00:07:08,360
what am I to you, truly?

113
00:07:12,720 --> 00:07:15,120
I always thought
you were deep and restrained,

114
00:07:18,120 --> 00:07:20,310
but you're no more than a hypocrite.

115
00:07:32,070 --> 00:07:33,000
If I hadn't noticed

116
00:07:33,000 --> 00:07:34,430
that you'd fallen for that guard,

117
00:07:35,160 --> 00:07:36,630
I would have spared his life.

118
00:07:39,680 --> 00:07:40,520
However,

119
00:07:41,480 --> 00:07:43,160
it's not impossible for me
to forgive him,

120
00:07:44,160 --> 00:07:45,900
as long as you agree
to one request of mine.

121
00:07:50,600 --> 00:07:51,440
What is it?

122
00:07:54,510 --> 00:07:55,630
From this day on,

123
00:07:56,560 --> 00:07:58,630
you shall stay by my side forever.

124
00:07:59,430 --> 00:08:00,830
You are never to see him again.

125
00:08:10,510 --> 00:08:11,430
Buddy,

126
00:08:11,720 --> 00:08:14,360
we really are destined to meet.

127
00:08:15,270 --> 00:08:18,480
You got lucky and survived last time,

128
00:08:19,720 --> 00:08:23,120
but luck won't save you today.

129
00:08:25,800 --> 00:08:27,240
End my life, then.

130
00:08:28,630 --> 00:08:29,510
End your life?

131
00:08:31,310 --> 00:08:32,670
That would be too easy.

132
00:08:33,750 --> 00:08:36,720
Even if your entire clan were executed,

133
00:08:37,500 --> 00:08:39,330
or even if nine generations
were exterminated,

134
00:08:39,810 --> 00:08:41,220
it would still be showing you mercy.

135
00:08:42,390 --> 00:08:43,670
I'm an orphan.

136
00:08:44,800 --> 00:08:46,270
There's no one left for you to punish.

137
00:08:47,600 --> 00:08:48,550
Do it.

138
00:08:49,510 --> 00:08:50,600
Then,

139
00:08:50,750 --> 00:08:53,750
you shall bear their sins
in their stead.

140
00:08:55,510 --> 00:08:58,480
I will make it so you live in agony,

141
00:08:59,240 --> 00:09:00,550
wishing for death.

142
00:09:03,510 --> 00:09:04,440
Stop.

143
00:09:06,120 --> 00:09:07,000
Lord Leng,

144
00:09:07,150 --> 00:09:07,990
what brings you here?

145
00:09:08,480 --> 00:09:09,670
Rest assured, My Lord.

146
00:09:10,000 --> 00:09:12,080
We carried out the punishment
as you ordered.

147
00:09:12,390 --> 00:09:13,910
Not a moment's delay.

148
00:09:15,030 --> 00:09:17,510
By His Majesty's decree,

149
00:09:18,270 --> 00:09:19,550
this man is pardoned.

150
00:09:19,750 --> 00:09:20,600
What?

151
00:09:28,030 --> 00:09:28,870
Leave this place,

152
00:09:29,750 --> 00:09:30,790
and never come back.

153
00:09:31,870 --> 00:09:33,320
Let go of those hopeless thoughts.

154
00:09:34,720 --> 00:09:36,270
Be the great hero you want to be.

155
00:09:38,480 --> 00:09:39,390
I want to see her.

156
00:09:45,120 --> 00:09:46,720
You barely escaped with your life.

157
00:09:47,510 --> 00:09:48,720
Set your heart free.

158
00:09:49,390 --> 00:09:50,360
If not,

159
00:09:51,000 --> 00:09:52,320
death will be your only path.

160
00:09:53,270 --> 00:09:54,120
I've already said so.

161
00:09:56,120 --> 00:09:57,200
I want to see her.

162
00:10:02,200 --> 00:10:03,040
Alright.

163
00:10:04,440 --> 00:10:06,910
In recognition of your past merits
in protecting him,

164
00:10:07,100 --> 00:10:09,440
the Emperor permits you
to see Her Highness one last time.

165
00:10:11,360 --> 00:10:12,200
However,

166
00:10:12,840 --> 00:10:14,000
after all, we have met once,

167
00:10:15,600 --> 00:10:17,110
I advise you to give up your illusions;

168
00:10:17,500 --> 00:10:18,480
it's better not to meet.

169
00:10:22,200 --> 00:10:23,480
In this world,

170
00:10:24,360 --> 00:10:26,670
many people can't see reality clearly,

171
00:10:28,240 --> 00:10:29,790
and you are no exception.

172
00:10:32,440 --> 00:10:33,280
Go now.

173
00:10:33,720 --> 00:10:34,720
The carriage up ahead,

174
00:10:35,860 --> 00:10:36,970
she's waiting for you there.

175
00:10:43,550 --> 00:10:44,550
Thank you.

176
00:11:21,600 --> 00:11:22,440
Qingyao.

177
00:11:26,120 --> 00:11:27,270
Seeing that you're safe,

178
00:11:28,630 --> 00:11:29,670
I can finally be at peace.

179
00:11:32,870 --> 00:11:33,710
I'm fine.

180
00:11:34,360 --> 00:11:35,200
How about you?

181
00:11:35,600 --> 00:11:36,440
How have you been?

182
00:11:36,670 --> 00:11:37,630
I've been doing well.

183
00:11:38,270 --> 00:11:39,320
During this time,

184
00:11:39,510 --> 00:11:40,840
I owe a lot to your help.

185
00:11:41,000 --> 00:11:41,840
I'm truly grateful.

186
00:11:45,170 --> 00:11:46,800
To my help, you say?

187
00:11:49,670 --> 00:11:51,150
W-what do you mean by that?

188
00:11:53,440 --> 00:11:54,280
Shiyi,

189
00:11:56,750 --> 00:11:57,590
we

190
00:12:00,220 --> 00:12:02,080
were never meant
to belong to the same world.

191
00:12:06,750 --> 00:12:07,910
What do you mean?

192
00:12:09,440 --> 00:12:10,790
I mean...

193
00:12:11,510 --> 00:12:12,350
Listen.

194
00:12:13,080 --> 00:12:14,240
You were born among commoners,

195
00:12:14,500 --> 00:12:16,110
while I live within the Imperial Palace.

196
00:12:16,480 --> 00:12:17,320
The two of us

197
00:12:17,320 --> 00:12:18,530
were brought together

198
00:12:18,530 --> 00:12:20,230
only because of this unexpected
incident.

199
00:12:21,600 --> 00:12:22,440
But now,

200
00:12:22,790 --> 00:12:24,360
I have become the Empress of the nation.

201
00:12:25,550 --> 00:12:28,030
We were never meant
to cross paths again.

202
00:12:28,270 --> 00:12:29,360
Do you understand that?

203
00:12:31,080 --> 00:12:31,920
I do.

204
00:12:35,670 --> 00:12:36,600
So,

205
00:12:37,440 --> 00:12:38,840
everything we went through before

206
00:12:40,790 --> 00:12:41,630
was all an illusion?

207
00:12:49,840 --> 00:12:51,080
In this world,

208
00:12:51,720 --> 00:12:53,080
there's no real or fake.

209
00:12:54,100 --> 00:12:55,270
Only this very moment matters.

210
00:12:58,750 --> 00:13:00,510
Well said.

211
00:13:02,910 --> 00:13:03,750
Hero Shi,

212
00:13:05,170 --> 00:13:06,570
you've saved my life more than once.

213
00:13:07,320 --> 00:13:09,480
I owe you a great debt.

214
00:13:10,510 --> 00:13:11,840
So now,

215
00:13:11,840 --> 00:13:13,200
I return your freedom to you.

216
00:13:16,440 --> 00:13:17,280
My heart

217
00:13:20,220 --> 00:13:21,390
can finally rest easy.

218
00:13:25,030 --> 00:13:26,080
So,

219
00:13:28,510 --> 00:13:30,080
are we completely even now?

220
00:13:35,550 --> 00:13:36,390
Yeah.

221
00:13:38,390 --> 00:13:39,230
You and I

222
00:13:39,700 --> 00:13:40,910
owe each other nothing anymore.

223
00:13:42,200 --> 00:13:43,720
The world is vast after all.

224
00:13:44,320 --> 00:13:45,360
From this day on,

225
00:13:47,720 --> 00:13:49,200
let's each walk our own path.

226
00:13:51,670 --> 00:13:53,080
So this wasn't a meeting,

227
00:13:55,320 --> 00:13:56,320
but a farewell.

228
00:14:01,870 --> 00:14:02,870
Hero Shi,

229
00:14:04,630 --> 00:14:05,600
we...

230
00:14:11,600 --> 00:14:13,000
Let's leave it at that.

231
00:14:19,960 --> 00:14:20,800
Your Highness,

232
00:14:22,480 --> 00:14:24,480
thank you for saving my life.

233
00:14:26,320 --> 00:14:27,160
Your Highness,

234
00:14:29,440 --> 00:14:30,480
I will take my leave.

235
00:15:06,450 --> 00:15:09,050
♪When a breeze passes by♪

236
00:15:09,570 --> 00:15:12,890
♪The sand and wind burn with longing♪

237
00:15:12,890 --> 00:15:15,530
♪Fearless even when thirst
goes unquenched♪

238
00:15:15,850 --> 00:15:19,010
♪Like a camel wandering
with eyes closed♪

239
00:15:19,370 --> 00:15:22,330
♪When the rain quietly settles♪

240
00:15:22,330 --> 00:15:25,650
♪I think of our sorrow yet unknown♪

241
00:15:25,850 --> 00:15:28,570
♪No need to hum the song of the wind♪

242
00:15:28,730 --> 00:15:32,370
♪Ignoring the sky darkening before us♪

243
00:15:32,530 --> 00:15:34,130
♪I finally understood that truth♪

244
00:15:34,130 --> 00:15:35,610
♪Yet you have already faded away♪

245
00:15:35,810 --> 00:15:37,450
♪I lose my way in the night♪

246
00:15:37,450 --> 00:15:38,930
♪Not knowing how to still my heart♪

247
00:15:38,930 --> 00:15:40,610
♪Loving you feels like lifetimes apart♪

248
00:15:40,610 --> 00:15:43,570
♪Yet longing flows back into verse♪

249
00:15:44,010 --> 00:15:46,450
♪For you and me to meet again♪

250
00:15:46,890 --> 00:15:49,730
♪We must cross a thousand years
of promises♪

251
00:15:50,010 --> 00:15:52,090
♪In the pouring rain♪

252
00:15:52,090 --> 00:15:56,450
♪As if you are still by my side♪
